data.meta_description: Bernard Garrick passed away in Naugatuck at age 94.  He was the husband of Ethel F. (Phillips) Garrick 1904-2000  Children: · Jane G. (Garrick) Page 1925-2004 · Mary Garrick · Bernard F. Garrick, Jr. 1933-2012 · Maureen P. 'Mo' (Garrick) Siuzdak 1939-2010  CEMETERY INFORMATION  Type of Marker: Headstone (monument) —...
